claim.claim-text:
1. A computer program product comprising: 
a computer storage medium and a computer program code mechanism embedded in the computer storage medium for causing a computer to forward a portion of a message to a wireless notification device using a private, non-commercial network, the computer program code mechanism comprising: 
a first computer code device configured to periodically connect to a remote information server to poll for new messages; 
a second computer code device configured to download a portion of each of the new messages; 
a third computer code device configured to transmit, for a subset of the new messages, the portion of the subset of messages using a private, non-commercial network.

19. An appliance control system comprising: 
a communications adapter for downloading information from a Wide-Area Network; 
a first non-commercial, private network transmitter for transmitting to at least one of a home appliance and an office appliance using at least one of a power-line carrier and a Bluetooth protocol to control the at least one of a home appliance and an office appliance; 
a microprocessor; and 
memory configured to control the microprocessor to control the communications adapter and the appliance transmitter.
